.hint-section#hintSection
  label.hint-label(for="hintInput") 💡 Additional Hint (optional):
  input.hint-input#hintInput(type="text" placeholder="e.g., specific model, condition, features, etc.")
  
  .additional-hints-section#additionalHintsSection
    label.hint-label(for="additionalHintsInput") 💡 Additional Hints for Sales Text (optional):
    input.hint-input#additionalHintsInput(type="text" placeholder="e.g., Product is in German, target audience, specific condition notes, etc.")
  
  .reset-section
    button.btn.btn-secondary#resetBtn 🔄 Start Over

